description: Come and enjoy our unique Food that originated in the heart and soul of New Orleans. The Crazy Creole Café catering truck, we are the café that rolls to you. We offer Authentic Creole and Cajun dishes. Most of our products are shipped in weekly from New Orleans, like our famous French bread, or the mayonaise we use on our po boys. We also serve Alligator, farm raised catfish, crawfish and more, all shipped in. We use only the best ingredients. Louisiana cuisine is at the heart of our unique culture. Created by the fusion of African, Native American and the European Ancestry. You are guaranteed to enjoy great flavors of my home town of Nawlins and we will show you what southern hospitality is all about. In New Orleans we have a saying "bon temp rollers" which means lets the good time roll. That is what our truck is all about. Good food & good music. We will do our best to put a big smile on your face and make you stomp your feet. So what are you waiting for? Come on and Bon temp rollers!
name: Crazy Creole Cafe
